00:13:10.280 --> 00:13:11.080
I understand.

00:13:12.480 --> 00:13:13.600
Not related to her?

00:13:13.920 --> 00:13:14.880
What do you think?

00:13:14.880 --> 00:13:16.210
Did you ever hate Wu Fei?

00:13:16.600 --> 00:13:17.530
What do you mean?

00:13:17.720 --> 00:13:18.640
You don't think

00:13:18.880 --> 00:13:20.160
I killed Wu Fei, do you?

00:13:20.320 --> 00:13:21.780
Just answer the question.

00:13:22.920 --> 00:13:23.980
I loved him so much.

00:13:25.320 --> 00:13:26.780
He was handsome and sweet.

00:13:26.960 --> 00:13:27.400
Plus,

00:13:27.520 --> 00:13:29.580
he handled every relationship well.

00:13:29.680 --> 00:13:31.140
before entering the next.

00:13:32.800 --> 00:13:33.800
As far as you know,

00:13:34.360 --> 00:13:35.480
does Wu Fei

00:13:35.840 --> 00:13:37.370
have any other girlfriends

00:13:37.520 --> 00:13:38.760
besides Su Na?

00:13:39.320 --> 00:13:41.520
He couldn't be involved with anyone else.

00:13:41.520 --> 00:13:42.760
He told me

00:13:42.760 --> 00:13:44.080
that I was his true love,

00:13:44.080 --> 00:13:45.320
his soulmate,

00:13:45.320 --> 00:13:46.680
and the person he cared about most

00:13:46.680 --> 00:13:47.760
in this world.

00:13:54.160 --> 00:13:54.680
Su Na,

00:13:57.000 --> 00:13:58.080
we wanted to ask

00:14:00.640 --> 00:14:02.320
what happened.

00:14:05.760 --> 00:14:07.600
We started dating a year ago.

00:14:08.560 --> 00:14:09.240
In between,

00:14:09.480 --> 00:14:11.760
we broke up and got back together many times.

00:14:11.760 --> 00:14:14.120
Then between you and Cao Wenwen...

00:14:14.760 --> 00:14:16.420
I was just teaching normally.

00:14:16.880 --> 00:14:18.760
After she got together with Wu Fei,

00:14:18.760 --> 00:14:20.220
she started targeting me.

00:14:22.160 --> 00:14:22.960
What happened to your hand?